* '''Teams Enabled''' - summons twelve circles to stand on in the lobby. More than one player can inhabit the same circle, guaranteeing to pair them with the same role as everyone in the circle, allowing there to be more than one Detective or Murderer.
* '''Scrambled Spawns''' - randomly selecting a room for players to start in the mansion, except the Detective always spawns in the Study.
* '''One Unlock Only''' - spawns one unlockable weapon for the first player to collect all five clues, and no more clues will spawn for anyone else.
* '''Invisible Knives''' is a game modifier that only allows the Murderer to see knives that are on the ground. Knives are still visible in the Murderer's hands.